    "1303201": {
        "Desc": "Go to the Mawtiyima Forest with Arapurva",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Um, Paimon's been meaning to ask what you meant by \"prepared.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arapurva",
                    "T": "Nara Avin has not completely remembered. Memories and dreams are both necessary."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Avin",
                    "T": "Dreams..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Avin",
                    "T": "But I'll never be able to stand again. Even if I can recover, I don't know how long that'll take."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arapurva",
                    "T": "Such worries are not needed here. Nara Avin, you must remember. Dreams are connected to your heart, not your body."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Avin",
                    "T": "My heart...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arapurva",
                    "T": "I led you this far, but now Nara Avin must find her precious things by herself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoimiya",
                    "T": "Huh? He's gone, just like that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoimiya",
                    "T": "It looks like the sky here has changed somewhat."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Avin",
                    "T": "My heart..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Avin",
                    "T": "...!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Avin",
                    "T": "I... stood up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Avin",
                    "T": "It wasn't hard at all, and it didn't feel weird. It was like... how things were before I got sick."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wait, so that means we're..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We're inside a dream."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Not our first time in one. Ah, no wonder Arapurva said not to worry... Avin can move freely in this dream."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Avin",
                    "T": "Wow, that's amazing, is this... the power of my heart?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoimiya",
                    "T": "How amazing! Now we can all look for Arashani together."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoimiya",
                    "T": "C'mon, let's race! Lemme see how good you really are!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Avin",
                    "T": "I might not have recovered yet..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Avin",
                    "T": "Whatever, let's go! I won't lose, not even to an adult!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ah, and off she goes!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, this was easy. Paimon thought she'd need more time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I guess that's what they call aptitude."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That's the power of a wish."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hehe, that's true. Let's catch up with them."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "1303215": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "1303202": {
        "Desc": "Catch up to Avin",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Avin",
                    "T": "*pants* You're... good..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoimiya",
                    "T": "Hehe, if we had run any further, you would've caught up!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Avin was neck and neck with Yoimiya!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Avin",
                    "T": "I've outrun lots of adults before. Long legs don't necessarily mean you run faster. Training's important, too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoimiya",
                    "T": "Haha, I won't even be able to compete with you in a few years."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoimiya",
                    "T": "Hm, let's see... Where should we go next?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ah, look! Something's floating up ahead!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It looks like a... star?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Avin",
                    "T": "Does it want us to follow it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoimiya",
                    "T": "Hmm, maybe. Let's follow it."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
